{"id":31232,"title":"Psychotic episode secondary to metronidazole use.","abstract":"Psychosis is a recognized but often forgotten side effect of many commonly prescribed medications.A case of psychosis in a 27-year-old female related to metronidazole treatment is presented along with review of possible mechanisms.The onset and resolution of psychosis appeared to coincide with metronidazole treatment.Clinicians should be aware of medication-related psychosis.","date":"2014-03-10","categories":"Chemically-Induced Disorders","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24388629","annotations":[{"name":"Pharmaceutical drug","weight":0.728515,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmaceutical_drug"},{"name":"Psychosis","weight":0.651405,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychosis"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.642761,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Side effect","weight":0.431085,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Side_effect"},{"name":"Clinic","weight":0.159066,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinic"},{"name":"Female","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Female"},{"name":"Metronidazole","weight":0.0274275,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metronidazole"},{"name":"Episode","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Episode"},{"name":"Texas Education Agency accountability ratings system","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Texas_Education_Agency_accountability_ratings_system"},{"name":"Absorption (pharmacokinetics)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Absorption_(pharmacokinetics)"},{"name":"Secondary school","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secondary_school"}]}
